---
title: Chorizo Koftas with Veggie Pilaf and Spiced Apple Chutney
description: We're trying out something new with the fan favourite, chorizo. Gently spiced chorizo gets formed into koftas and is paired with a veggie pilaf and apple chutney to create a gorgeous aromatic plate with sweetness and balance.
